---
import "../../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>AIR Locomotion - Xi Lin</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-white text-gray-900">
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16 sm:px-10">
      <a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-900">Back to home</a>
      <p class="mt-6 text-sm font-mono text-blue-600">Tsinghua University AIR | Embodied AI Research Intern</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">Humanoid Locomotion in Complex Terrain</h1>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-4xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
        At AIR, I worked on humanoid robot motion control in complex terrain. The project included parameterized terrain generation in Isaac Gym, curriculum-based RL training, and sim-to-real deployment from simulation to Unitree H1 through ROS2.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 overflow-hidden rounded-[28px] border border-gray-200 bg-black">
        <video controls playsinline class="w-full">
          <source src="/assets/projects/air-h1-demo.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
      </div>

      <section class="mt-10 rounded-[28px] border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Program Core</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
          <li>Built stair, slope, and other terrain variants in Isaac Gym to improve humanoid adaptability to complex environments.</li>
          <li>Used curriculum-based RL training to advance difficulty progressively, improving convergence speed, gait stability, and robustness.</li>
          <li>Deployed the trained locomotion policy from simulation to Unitree H1 through ROS2 control nodes, while keeping the system extensible to real-time SLAM tasks.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {["Isaac Gym", "ROS2", "RL", "SLAM", "Terrain Sim", "PPO"].map((item) => (
            <span class="rounded-full border border-gray-300 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
              {item}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
